OL,3,CGuernsey's Head of the Public Service
OL,4,Cto step down in 2025
OL,6,FGuernsey's Head of the Public Service
OL,7,Fhas announced he intends to step down
OL,8,Fbefore the island's General Election
OL,9,Fnext year.
OL,11,FMark de Garis has spent the last 40
OL,12,Fyears working in Guernsey's civil
OL,13,Fservice and says he wanted to give
OL,14,Fplenty of advance notice, so a
OL,15,Fsuccessor can be put in place ahead of
OL,16,Fthe election.
