OL,3,CGuernsey's Head of the Public Service
OL,4,Cto step down in 2025
OL,6,FSpeaking about his decision, he said:
OL,7,F'It has been the privilege of my
OL,8,Fcareer to serve as the Head of the
OL,9,FPublic Service and I am very grateful
OL,10,Fto all of my colleagues who have
OL,11,Fsupported me in this challenging but
OL,12,Fhugely rewarding role.
OL,14,F'When I first joined the civil service
OL,15,Fin the 1980s, I couldn't have imagined
OL,16,Fthe opportunities that this
OL,17,Forganisation would provide me and I am
OL,18,Fso proud of the public sector and the
OL,19,Fdedication that I see each and every
OL,20,Fday.'
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
