OL,3,CGuernsey's Head of the Public Service
OL,4,Cto step down in 2025
OL,6,FHe added: 'When I accepted the role of
OL,7,FHead of the Public Service I was clear
OL,8,Fthat my intention was to support the
OL,9,Fcurrent political body during an
OL,10,Fimmensely challenging time but that I
OL,11,Fwas unable to commit to the next
OL,12,Fpolitical term.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
