CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1722409049
OL,3,CGuernsey's Head of the Public Service
OL,4,Cto step down in 2025
OL,6,F'With the election now less than one
OL,7,Fyear away I was keen to provide early
OL,8,Fnotice that I would be stepping down
OL,9,Fin 2025 in order that my successor is
OL,10,Fin post and I am able to provide a
OL,11,Fdetailed and structured handover to
OL,12,Fensure they are in the best possible
OL,13,Fposition to support the incoming
OL,14,FAssembly.'
OL,16,FDep Lyndon Trott, President of the
OL,17,FPolicy and Resources Committee, said:
OL,18,F'I want to take this opportunity to
OL,19,Fthank Mark for his exemplary
OL,20,Fcommitment to the public service over
OL,21,Fhid distinguished career.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
