PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1722409049
OL,3,CGuernsey's Head of the Public Service
OL,4,Cto step down in 2025
OL,6,F'By the very nature of the public
OL,7,Fservice, much of his work has, by
OL,8,Fnecessity, taken place behind the
OL,9,Fscenes but he has been integral to
OL,10,Fmany of the most important steps taken
OL,11,Fby government over the last decade.
OL,13,F'I speak on behalf of the whole
OL,14,Fcommittee, and I'm sure wider
OL,15,Fcolleagues, when I say how much we
OL,16,Fhave valued Mark's support and advice
OL,17,Fand we wish ghim the very best for his
OL,18,Fretirement'.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
