OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1722409049
OL,3,CGuernsey's Head of the Public Service
OL,4,Cto step down in 2025
OL,6,FDep Trott added: 'While Mark's
OL,7,Fdeparture will be a significant loss
OL,8,Fto the organisation, we will shortly
OL,9,Fbe launching a recruitment campaign
OL,10,Ffor his successor.
OL,12,F'We hope to make an appointment during
OL,13,Fthe autumn in order to provide a
OL,14,Fsuccessful transition early in 2025.'
